fvwm3 (1.0.8+ds-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release.
  * Remove debian/desktop/fvwm3.desktop in favor of upstream file.
  * Add patch to add Keywords and Icon to fvwm3.desktop.
  * Add bin/FvwmPrompt/FvwmPrompt to FilesExcluded in debian/copyright
    due to the binary accidentally added to release tarball.

